Interface IScriptTaskType.IProjectScriptTaskType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IScriptTaskType, IUserMessage
    Enclosing interface:
    IScriptTaskType

    @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public static interface IScriptTaskType.IProjectScriptTaskType
extends IScriptTaskType
    The IScriptTaskType.IProjectScriptTaskType marks the IScriptTask to be a task for EScriptTaskCategory#PROJECT. This is used to provide overloaded methods in interface for the different types.
